<html>
<head>
<style>body{font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif}</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="main">
	<a href="<%= siteURL %>"><img src="<%= url.resolve(siteURL, 'resource/images/logo.png')%>" alt="OpenHIE ID"></a>
	<h2>This email address requires verification.</h2>
	
<p><%= displayName %>,</p>	

<p>Thanks for updating your OpenHIE ID!</p>

<p>Since you have provided a new email address, <strong><%= email %></strong>, we need to verify it before it can be used to subscribe to mailing lists, receive communication from community tools, and appear on your profile.</p>

<p>To verify your address, go to the following page:</p>
<p><a href="<%= url.resolve(siteURL, '/'+urlBase+'/'+verifyId) %>"><%= url.resolve(siteURL, '/'+urlBase+'/'+verifyId) %></a></p>

<p>In case of problems managing your account or logging in, please email us at <a href="mailto:support@ohie.org">support@ohie.org</a> &mdash; remember to include your contact information so we can assist you.</p>

<p>If you received this message in error, don't worry. <%= displayName %> will not be able to utilize this address without going through the verification process above.</p>

<p>Thanks!</p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
